<br /><br />

<p class="font-fam3 tuth2">Save</p>	
<p class="tuta">Use <%= image_tag('export2.png', :class => "exportimg") %> to save your hall. (Apple users should hold image down after export to save hall then navigate back to editor). Scroll down and select next. </p> 
<br /><br />

<p class="font-fam3 tuth2">Frequent issues</p>
<p class=" tuta">If you have trouble scrolling the editor, swipe from the head or base and scroll.</p>	
<p class=" tuta">If you notice your text is truncated, leave a space above text in the textbox as seen above.</p>
